snippet.title: 24x365 News
snippet.description:
24x365 News brings you up-to-the-minute global news video, often ahead of the mainstream news channels.  Subscribe now and watch as the stories unfold.

We encourage debate and feedback.  Spam, bullying and offensive comments will be removed, and repeat offenders will be banned from the channel.
